msgid "<refentrytitle>&create_makefiles;</refentrytitle>"
msgstr "<refentrytitle>&create_makefiles;</refentrytitle> इति"

#. Tag: manvolnum
#: man-create_makefiles.1.docbook:14
#, no-c-format
msgid "<manvolnum>1</manvolnum>"
msgstr "<मन्वोल्नुम्>१</मन्वोल्नुम्>"

#. Tag: refname
#: man-create_makefiles.1.docbook:18
#, no-c-format
msgid "<refname>&create_makefiles;</refname>"
msgstr "<refname>&create_makefiles;</refname> इति"

#. Tag: refpurpose
#: man-create_makefiles.1.docbook:19
#, no-c-format
msgid "Recreates all <filename>Makefile</filename>s beneath a directory"
msgstr "निर्देशिकायाः अधः सर्वाणि <filename>Makefile</filename>s पुनः निर्माति"

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: man-create_makefiles.1.docbook:23
#, no-c-format
msgid "&create_makefiles; <group><replaceable>dir</replaceable></group>"
msgstr "&create_makefiles; <group><replaceable>dir</replaceable></group> इति"

#. Tag: title
#: man-create_makefiles.1.docbook:31
#, no-c-format
msgid "Description"
msgstr "वर्णनम्‌"

#. Tag: para
#: man-create_makefiles.1.docbook:33
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&create_makefiles; recreates all <filename>Makefile</filename>s in "
"<replaceable>dir</replaceable> and its (recursed) subdirectories from the "
"corresponding <filename>Makefile.am</filename> templates."
msgstr ""
"&create_makefiles; <replaceable>dir</replaceable> इत्यस्मिन् सर्वाणि "
"<filename>Makefile</filename>s तथा तस्य (पुनरावृत्तिः) उपनिर्देशिकाः तत्सम्बद्धेभ्यः "
"<filename>Makefile.am</filename> टेम्पलेट् इत्यस्मात् पुनः सृजति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: man-create_makefiles.1.docbook:38
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This script must be run from the toplevel directory (the one containing "
"configure). This script saves time compared to re-running configure "
"completely."
msgstr ""
"इयं स्क्रिप्ट् toplevel निर्देशिकातः (configure युक्तात्) चालनीया । एषा स्क्रिप्ट् पूर्णतया "
"विन्यासस्य पुनः चालनस्य तुलने समयस्य रक्षणं करोति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: man-create_makefiles.1.docbook:42
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the source directory is different from the build directory (see the "
"environment variables below), it will be assumed that each "
"<filename>Makefile.am</filename> and <filename>Makefile.in</filename> "
"belongs beneath the source directory and that each <filename>Makefile</"
"filename> belongs beneath the build directory."
msgstr ""
"यदि स्रोतनिर्देशिका निर्माणनिर्देशिकातः भिन्ना अस्ति (अधः वातावरणचराः पश्यन्तु), तर्हि "
"प्रत्येकं <filename>Makefile.am</filename> तथा <filename>Makefile.in</filename> "
"इत्येतत् स्रोतनिर्देशिकायाः अधः अस्ति इति कल्प्यते तथा च प्रत्येकं <filename>Makefile</"
"filename> निर्माणनिर्देशिकायाः अधः अस्ति इति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: man-create_makefiles.1.docbook:49
#, no-c-format
msgid "This utility is part of the &kde; Software Development Kit."
msgstr "एषा उपयोगिता &kde; सॉफ्टवेयर विकास किट।"

#. Tag: title
#: man-create_makefiles.1.docbook:54
#, no-c-format
msgid "Environment"
msgstr "पर्यावरणम्‌"

#. Tag: para
#: man-create_makefiles.1.docbook:55
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"One of the following variables (but not both) should be set if the source "
"directory is different from the build directory. If the build directory is "
"simply a subdirectory of the source directory, the simpler variable "
"<envar>OBJ_SUBDIR</envar> should be used."
msgstr ""
"यदि स्रोतनिर्देशिका build निर्देशिकातः भिन्ना अस्ति तर्हि निम्नलिखितचरानाम् एकः (किन्तु "
"उभयत्र न) सेट् कर्तव्यः । यदि build निर्देशिका केवलं स्रोतनिर्देशिकायाः उपनिर्देशिका अस्ति "
"तर्हि सरलतरं चरं <envar>OBJ_SUBDIR</envar> उपयोक्तव्यम् ।"

#. Tag: envar
#: man-create_makefiles.1.docbook:62
#, no-c-format
msgid "OBJ_SUBJDIR"
msgstr "OBJ_SUBJDIR"

#. Tag: para
#: man-create_makefiles.1.docbook:63
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Indicates that the build directory is in the given subdirectory of the "
"source directory. For instance, if the source directory is <filename class="
"\"directory\">kdesdk</filename> and the build directory is <filename class="
"\"directory\">kdesdk/obj-i386-linux</filename>, then <envar>OBJ_SUBDIR</"
"envar> should be set to <parameter>obj-i386-linux</parameter>."
msgstr ""
"build directory स्रोतनिर्देशिकायाः दत्ते उपनिर्देशिकायां अस्ति इति सूचयति । यथा, यदि "
"स्रोतनिर्देशिका <filename class=\"directory\">kdesdk</filename> अस्ति तथा च "
"निर्माणनिर्देशिका <filename class=\"directory\">kdesdk/obj-i386-linux</"
"filename> अस्ति, तर्हि <envar> OBJ_SUBDIR</envar> इत्येतत् <parameter>obj-i386-"
"linux</parameter> इति सेट् कर्तव्यम् ।"

#. Tag: envar
#: man-create_makefiles.1.docbook:66
#, no-c-format
msgid "OBJ_REPLACEMENT"
msgstr "OBJ_REPLACEMENT इति"

#. Tag: para
#: man-create_makefiles.1.docbook:67
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A <command>sed</command> expression that is used to transform the source "
"directory into the build directory. For instance, if the source directory is "
"<filename class=\"directory\">kdesdk/obj-i386-linux</filename>, then "
"<envar>OBJ_REPLACEMENT</envar> should be set to <parameter>s#kdesdk#kdesdk-"
"obj#</parameter>."
msgstr ""
"एकं <command>sed</command> व्यञ्जनं यत् स्रोतनिर्देशिकायाः निर्माणनिर्देशिकायां "
"परिवर्तनार्थं उपयुज्यते । यथा, यदि स्रोतनिर्देशिका <filename class=\"directory"
"\">kdesdk/obj-i386-linux</filename> अस्ति, तर्हि <envar>OBJ_REPLACEMENT</"
"envar> इति <parameter>s#kdesdk#kdesdk- इति सेट् कर्तव्यम् । obj#</parameter> इति ।"

